kinds of applications which live in the cloud, so that we &lt;strong&gt;minimize the operating cost&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VC for Cloud is challenging problem till today. Addressing those issues and providing
possible solution design is our goal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;The end product will have many benefits, for example, an organization can minimize the Power bills and donate monetary credits to Volunteers.&lt;/p&gt;
